data.description: This K Hovnanian Home showcases the sought-after stone and brick exteriors in this enchanting community.   As you step inside, you will be welcomed by the large foyer with ceramic wood-look flooring. This home features an open-concept layout that seamlessly connects the living and dining areas, creating an ideal space for entertaining both family and guests. The kitchen features granite counters with a spacious island. This split plan includes 3 bedrooms, along with an additional office space that boasts French doors. The primary en-suite offers double sinks, a garden tub, a separate shower, and a generously sized walk-in closet. Enjoy the covered back patio and the home's cul-de-sac location is great for kids to play. Convenient access to major highways adds to the appeal. Schedule your appointment today!
